Something Wicked This Way Comes ⚡️😈⚡️
About 6 years ago I went over to @thetylerbryant and @caleb_crosby rehearsal space in Nashville TN and jammed with them and wrote some really special songs . I walked out of those sessions and was like well damn that was pure magic !! Flash forward to this year I reached out to Tyler and was like hey do y’all want to do a concept record with me loosely based on the book of Revelations? Tyler and Caleb were like heck yea buddy !  We then proceeded to make an ASTOUNDINGlY. EPIC .HEAVY. ASS .ROCK RECORD!!!! This record sounds so huge, aggressive and soulful! I cannot thank Tyler and Caleb enough for bringing this crazy vision to life in such BIG BIG WAY !! Everyone dove into this project headfirst and created something really really special that we cannot wait for y’all to hear . It sounds like Soundgarden/Audioslave mixed with early Ozzy and later Dio Black Sabbath sprinkled with some theatricality in the vein of Queen/Meat Loaf ! There is also an almost 7 minute instrumental rock opera piece that Tyler and Caleb absolutely CRUSHED!! Can’t wait for y’all to hear this amazing work of art !!

Appreciate all the birthday love today 🤘❤️🤘!! 32 years old !! My, my how the time flys !!! Lots of exciting stuff happening this year ! Got some AMAZING new music for y’all  and can’t wait to perform in 🇬🇧 UK for the first time next month!! Much love and rock on ⚡️🤘
